reviewText: This is a great workout and meditation from a Catholic worldview.  I took one star off because there was only one workout on the video.  It would have been nice to have complete workouts, start to finish, in different time increments (30 minutes vs. 60 minutes).  Having only one workout on the video makes it kind of expensive compared to other workouts on the market.  Overall, it was very peaceful yet challenging enough to keep me engaged and focused.
